content.rendered:
BOSS AIR AIRLOCKER UPGRADE KIT

Boss Air Airlocker Upgrade Kit available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Upgrade your onboard air kit and have a separate regulated air flow to your air locker without changing your existing pressure switch.

To view the full range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!

For more 4×4 inspiration follow us on Instagram and Facebook
